1.Testing Shows Presence of Defects:
Functional Defect
Non Functional Defect
GUI Defect
Security Defect

2.Exhaustive testing is impossible:
Every Combination of input are not possible to check

3.Early Testing:
Static Testing

4.Defect Clustering:
When Two or more itmes are there make sure one will effect another

5.Pasticide Paradox:
Regularly review and revised something

6.Testing is context dependent:
Testing is dependent on project

7.Absence of Error Fallacy:
If Error is solved or not present but your requirement are not fullfilled

